    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>RANK SELLS UNIVERSAL STAKE</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Alan Cowell</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Cowell, Alan</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Blackstone Capital Partners LP agrees to purchase Rank Group's 50 percent ownership of Florida-based Universal Studios Escape theme park for $275 million cash (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A United States venture capital firm, Blackstone Capital Partners L.P., said it had agreed to buy the Rank Group's 50 percent stake in the Florida-based theme park Universal Studios Escape for $275 million in cash. Rank, the owner of the Hard Rock Cafe chain, may receive a further $75 million if the theme park meets profit targets. Rank is streamlining its leisure division as part of efforts to reduce debt.</p>
        <p>Alan Cowell</p>
      </block>
